  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To explore effectiveness of procalcitonin-guided antibiotic therapy in acute exacerbations of
      bronchiectasis, and to explore the clinical value of procalcitonin in bronchiectasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
